{"title":"CyclingCeramic Lowers the Cost of Free Watts","link":"https://bikerumor.com/cyclingceramic-lowers-the-cost-of-free-watts/","date":1693847600000,"content":"<p><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/CyclingCeramic-rear-derailleur-upgrades-get-more-affordable_OSPW-on-SRAM-Rival-AXS.jpg\" alt=\"CyclingCeramic rear derailleur upgrades get more affordable, Oversize Cage on SRAM Rival AXS\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/CyclingCeramic-rear-derailleur-upgrades-get-more-affordable_OSPW-on-SRAM-Rival-AXS.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/CyclingCeramic-rear-derailleur-upgrades-get-more-affordable_OSPW-on-SRAM-Rival-AXS-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/CyclingCeramic-rear-derailleur-upgrades-get-more-affordable_OSPW-on-SRAM-Rival-AXS-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/CyclingCeramic-rear-derailleur-upgrades-get-more-affordable_OSPW-on-SRAM-Rival-AXS-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/CyclingCeramic-rear-derailleur-upgrades-get-more-affordable_OSPW-on-SRAM-Rival-AXS-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/CyclingCeramic-rear-derailleur-upgrades-get-more-affordable_OSPW-on-SRAM-Rival-AXS-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/CyclingCeramic-rear-derailleur-upgrades-get-more-affordable_OSPW-on-SRAM-Rival-AXS-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>French ceramic bearing and oversized derailleur pulley maker CyclingCeramic drops the cost of buying those ‘Free Watts’ to make your bike’s drivetrain faster. You get the same carbon cages, machined alloy pulleys &amp; ceramic bearing kits or simply derailleur pulley wheels themselves for 20% less cash outlay, thanks to improved manufacturing efficiencies…</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>CyclingCeramic rear derailleur upgrades get more affordable</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/CyclingCeramic-ODC-14-19T-carbon-titanium-ceramic-bearing-oversized-derailleur-cage-upgrade-kit.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/CyclingCeramic-ODC-14-19T-carbon-titanium-ceramic-bearing-oversized-derailleur-cage-upgrade-kit-800x533.jpg\" alt srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/CyclingCeramic-ODC-14-19T-carbon-titanium-ceramic-bearing-oversized-derailleur-cage-upgrade-kit-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/CyclingCeramic-ODC-14-19T-carbon-titanium-ceramic-bearing-oversized-derailleur-cage-upgrade-kit-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/CyclingCeramic-ODC-14-19T-carbon-titanium-ceramic-bearing-oversized-derailleur-cage-upgrade-kit-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/CyclingCeramic-ODC-14-19T-carbon-titanium-ceramic-bearing-oversized-derailleur-cage-upgrade-kit-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/CyclingCeramic-ODC-14-19T-carbon-titanium-ceramic-bearing-oversized-derailleur-cage-upgrade-kit-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/CyclingCeramic-ODC-14-19T-carbon-titanium-ceramic-bearing-oversized-derailleur-cage-upgrade-kit-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/CyclingCeramic-ODC-14-19T-carbon-titanium-ceramic-bearing-oversized-derailleur-cage-upgrade-kit.jpg 1800w\" /></a><figcaption><em>all c. CyclingCeramic</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>More speed, for less money. Win, win, right? </p>\n\n\n\n<p>According to CyclingCeramic, it comes down to overall optimization of how they produce their pulley wheels and cage upgrade kits, as well as improved economies of scale from actually selling more upgrades. That meant they could deliver the same quality for less. And so they are passing on those savings. That’s then more than 20% off discount for their popular Oversize Cage kits and replacement Pulley Wheels.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>No compromises on quality or durability, just improved manufacturing efficiency. And their upgrades are still handcrafted in France.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>How much do you save?</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/CyclingCeramic-rear-derailleur-upgrades-more-affordable_pulley-wheels-colors.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"267\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/CyclingCeramic-rear-derailleur-upgrades-more-affordable_pulley-wheels-colors-800x267.jpg\" alt=\"CyclingCeramic rear derailleur upgrades get more affordable, pulley wheels in colors\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/CyclingCeramic-rear-derailleur-upgrades-more-affordable_pulley-wheels-colors-800x267.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/CyclingCeramic-rear-derailleur-upgrades-more-affordable_pulley-wheels-colors-297x99.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/CyclingCeramic-rear-derailleur-upgrades-more-affordable_pulley-wheels-colors-120x40.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/CyclingCeramic-rear-derailleur-upgrades-more-affordable_pulley-wheels-colors-768x256.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/CyclingCeramic-rear-derailleur-upgrades-more-affordable_pulley-wheels-colors-1536x512.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/CyclingCeramic-rear-derailleur-upgrades-more-affordable_pulley-wheels-colors.jpg 1800w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>That then means their standard 11 &amp; 12T machined alloy replacement Pulley Wheels with ceramic bearings now sell from 99€, down from 125€ for the pair. Pick from 11- or 12-speed replacement pulleys for Campagnolo Chorus, Record &amp; Super Record; Shimano 105, Ultegra &amp; Dura-Ace; and SRAM AXS Road. Or choose their slightly more expensive (but still cheaper than before) Narrow (<em>&amp; wide</em>) 14T replacements for on- &amp; off-road. Choose from Shimano GRX, XT &amp; XTR and SRAM Road, XPLR gravel &amp; Eagle MTB. Get ’em all in black, blue, gold, or reed ano for a little derailleur customization.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/CyclingCeramic-ODC-14-19T-carbon-titanium-ceramic-bearing-oversized-derailleur-cage-upgrade-kit_Shimano-colors.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"288\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/CyclingCeramic-ODC-14-19T-carbon-titanium-ceramic-bearing-oversized-derailleur-cage-upgrade-kit_Shimano-colors-800x288.jpg\" alt=\"CyclingCeramic ODC 14-19T carbon titanium ceramic bearing oversized derailleur cage upgrade kit, Shimano colors\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/CyclingCeramic-ODC-14-19T-carbon-titanium-ceramic-bearing-oversized-derailleur-cage-upgrade-kit_Shimano-colors-800x288.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/CyclingCeramic-ODC-14-19T-carbon-titanium-ceramic-bearing-oversized-derailleur-cage-upgrade-kit_Shimano-colors-297x107.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/CyclingCeramic-ODC-14-19T-carbon-titanium-ceramic-bearing-oversized-derailleur-cage-upgrade-kit_Shimano-colors-120x43.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/CyclingCeramic-ODC-14-19T-carbon-titanium-ceramic-bearing-oversized-derailleur-cage-upgrade-kit_Shimano-colors-768x276.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/CyclingCeramic-ODC-14-19T-carbon-titanium-ceramic-bearing-oversized-derailleur-cage-upgrade-kit_Shimano-colors-1536x553.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/CyclingCeramic-ODC-14-19T-carbon-titanium-ceramic-bearing-oversized-derailleur-cage-upgrade-kit_Shimano-colors.jpg 2000w\" /></a><figcaption>CyclingCeramic ODC 14/19T</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, their Oversize Cage kit consisting of carbon cages with oversized machined alloy pulleys and ceramic bearings now sell for 269€, down from 349€. So, there you can upgrade almost all Campy, Shimano &amp; SRAM road and gravel rear derailleurs. Then, get bigger 14 &amp; 19T pulleys for decreased drag – and in some pretty colors, too.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/CyclingCeramic-ODC-14-19T-carbon-titanium-ceramic-bearing-oversized-derailleur-cage-upgrade-kit_photo-by-Alexis-Sicard_SRAM-detail.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/CyclingCeramic-ODC-14-19T-carbon-titanium-ceramic-bearing-oversized-derailleur-cage-upgrade-kit_photo-by-Alexis-Sicard_SRAM-detail-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"CyclingCeramic ODC 14-19T carbon titanium ceramic bearing oversized derailleur cage upgrade kit, photo by Alexis Sicard, triathlon detail\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/CyclingCeramic-ODC-14-19T-carbon-titanium-ceramic-bearing-oversized-derailleur-cage-upgrade-kit_photo-by-Alexis-Sicard_SRAM-detail-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/CyclingCeramic-ODC-14-19T-carbon-titanium-ceramic-bearing-oversized-derailleur-cage-upgrade-kit_photo-by-Alexis-Sicard_SRAM-detail-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/CyclingCeramic-ODC-14-19T-carbon-titanium-ceramic-bearing-oversized-derailleur-cage-upgrade-kit_photo-by-Alexis-Sicard_SRAM-detail-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/CyclingCeramic-ODC-14-19T-carbon-titanium-ceramic-bearing-oversized-derailleur-cage-upgrade-kit_photo-by-Alexis-Sicard_SRAM-detail-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/CyclingCeramic-ODC-14-19T-carbon-titanium-ceramic-bearing-oversized-derailleur-cage-upgrade-kit_photo-by-Alexis-Sicard_SRAM-detail-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/CyclingCeramic-ODC-14-19T-carbon-titanium-ceramic-bearing-oversized-derailleur-cage-upgrade-kit_photo-by-Alexis-Sicard_SRAM-detail.jpg 1500w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>CyclingCeramic maintains their “Flexible Return Policy” with attention to minimizing the risk of trying something new. Additionally, they’ve even extended warranties from 2 to 4 years for all products now, making the buying decision even easier.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Free Watts just got a little more affordable.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://cyclingceramic.com/\" target=\"_blank\">CyclingCeramic.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/cyclingceramic-lowers-the-cost-of-free-watts/\">CyclingCeramic Lowers the Cost of Free Watts</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"c909b88143b74119d2ec6d0377d280df77d1aee04e60dddc431ee2a4d0f9a1fa","category":"Cycling"}